2025-05-07 11:26:50 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1746617210,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"212.180.196.145","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/135.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10838,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1587","nick":"Jacek","topic":"Dotyczy zmian w projekcie Tango IV","content":"Szanowni Pa\u0144stwo, prosz\u0119 o informacj\u0119 ile kosztuje u Pa\u0144stwa zmiana \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a ogrzewania z pieca gazowego na piec na paliwo sta\u0142e oraz zmian\u0119 usytuowania tarasu. Chodzi mi aby wyj\u015bcie na taras taras by\u01420 od lewej strony (od strony oznaczonego wymiaru 6,8). Prosz\u0119 r\u00f3wnie\u017c o podanie powierzchni zabudowy.","create_date":"2025-05-07 11:26:50","modify_date":"2025-05-07 11:26:50","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2774575},"entity_changes":false}
